Interface IState

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ComputingRouteState, DefaultState, DeliverySelectedState, EmptyNodeSelectedState, InitState, MapLoadedState, MapSelectState, NothingSelectedState, PlanningLoadedState, PlanningSelectState, SelectionsStates, SwapDeliveriesState, WarehouseSelectedState

    public interface IState
    This interface defines all the methods that should be implemented by logical states.
